<p><strong>Name:</strong> ItsDenali / Denali</p>
<p><strong>Base of Operations:</strong> USA</p>
<p><strong>Position:</strong> Graphic Design Student, writer (duh), photographer, geology junkie, and bison enthusiast</p>
<p><strong>History:</strong> ItsDenali, (or Denali for brevity's sake) first discovered the SCP Wiki in the summer of 2018 via a series of memes that made him wonder what the an ess-see-pee was and why people were obsessing over an pissed-off, spray-painted peanut. By late summer he had at last joined the SCP Foundation Site. Through several episodes of trial and error of getting to know the Wiki and how it worked, as well as a cringey, failed article, he surged back up on August 26th, 2018 having produced his first surviving mainlist article.</p>
<p>Denali continues to post SCPs to this day, chipping away at them whenever he has time, always looking for ways for them to reference each other and obscure details about his personal life, and severely over-analyzing every last detail before posting.</p>
